skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny fact
des:
Ask for Random Facts of Fun, and learn about what are the funny stories about this world.

 Facts of Fun provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Funny Facts" or "Alexa, open Funny Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
